Detailed Description

An alternative word spelling suggestion.

Equality, Hashing, and Copying

WNSpellingSuggestion instances implement NSObject's hash and isEqual methods, as well as the NSCopying protocol. Instances may be compared by value using NSObject::isEqual: and may be used as a key in NSDictionary.
